From: Siddharth Heroor <heroor@ti.com>
Date: Wed, 21 Sep 2011 08:22:49 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 11/12] ti814x: Change start-stop-daemon to use $matrixgui

* Intermittent failures seen when using pid.

Signed-off-by: Siddharth Heroor <heroor@ti.com>
---
 trunk/ti814x/etc/init |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/trunk/ti814x/etc/init b/trunk/ti814x/etc/init
index b48578b..93cf866 100644
--- a/trunk/ti814x/etc/init
+++ b/trunk/ti814x/etc/init
@@ -40,7 +40,7 @@ case "$1" in
 
   stop)
     echo -n "Stopping Matrix GUI application"
-    start-stop-daemon --stop --quiet --pidfile /var/run/matrix-gui-e.pid
+    start-stop-daemon --stop --quiet --exec $matrixgui
     echo "."
     ;;
   *)
